# Clean-Code-Chapter-7



* there is tow error in programming  : 
1 - error : not recoverable  and caused by system memory error , annonation error .. etc
2- exception :  recoverable  caused by application code like file not found, time  etc 



** using exception 
1 -  make the program to stop 
2 -code is cleaner with exception than with  errors 



** using error 
1- doesnt make the program tos top 
2- errors mmust be handled 



*exception is perfered  errors



*  dont return null 


*design your special case (method) well 



* dont pass null to method 
